                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Piyuṭim</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">פיוטים</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Folio 95 contains the beginning of an alphabetical index of the piyuṭim collected in the volume, with indications of folios and pages. The opening wordsof several pieces that stodd in the missing nine folios at the beginning have thus been preserved. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Folios 87v-88v contain a poem in Arabic in Hebrew characters on the death of a woman martyr. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>On folio 89r is a Hebrew love poem, written in a different hand. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
